OL,3,CBritain is 'sick man of Europe' ` new
OL,4,Creport into health of the nation
OL,6,FBritain is the "sick man of Europe"
OL,7,Fwhen it comes to health, according to
OL,8,Fa new report which highlights serious
OL,9,Fconcerns about a rise in the number of
OL,10,Fpeople off work due to long-term
OL,11,Fillness.
OL,13,FHealth challenges facing the nation
OL,14,Fhave reached "historic proportions",
OL,15,Faccording to the Institute for Public
OL,16,FPolicy Research (IPPR).
OL,18,FResearchers point to a stark rise in
OL,19,Fpeople who are missing from the
OL,20,Fworkplace due to long-term illness
OL,21,Fsince 2020.
