OL,3,CBritain is 'sick man of Europe' ` new
OL,4,Creport into health of the nation
OL,6,F"While it is hard to predict whether
OL,7,Fincreases in economic inactivity due
OL,8,Fto sickness will plateau or continue
OL,9,Fto grow in coming years, should the
OL,10,Frate of growth continue at the same
OL,11,Fpace it has since 2020, we would
OL,12,Fexpect economic inactivity due to
OL,13,Fsickness to reach 4.3 million by the
OL,14,Fend of the next parliament," the
OL,15,Fresearchers said.
OL,17,FIt comes as part of the final report
OL,18,Fof the IPPR's Commission on Health and
OL,19,FProsperity.
