OL,3,CBritain is 'sick man of Europe' ` new
OL,4,Creport into health of the nation
OL,6,FThe Commission is co-chaired by Lord
OL,7,FDarzi ` who recently led a hard-
OL,8,Fhitting review into the state of the
OL,9,FNHS for the Government ` and England's
OL,10,Fformer chief medical officer,
OL,11,FProfessor Dame Sally Davies.
OL,13,FLord Darzi's wide-ranging review,
OL,14,Fpublished last week, concluded that
OL,15,Fthe NHS is "in serious trouble" and
OL,16,Fhas prompted Labour to promise wide-
OL,17,Fspread reform of the health service.
