OL,4,Creport into health of the nation
OL,6,FNow the new IPPR report also
OL,7,Fhighlights how long-term illness is
OL,8,Fimpacting productivity and the labour
OL,9,Fsupply.
OL,11,F"The term the 'sick man of Europe' is
OL,12,Foften used to describe countries going
OL,13,Fthrough severe economic turmoil or
OL,14,Fsocial unrest. In Britain today, it
OL,15,Fhas become a more literal reality,"
OL,16,Fthe authors wrote.
