OL,3,CBritain is 'sick man of Europe' ` new
OL,4,Creport into health of the nation
OL,6,FThe authors suggest that better
OL,7,Fpopulation health could save the NHS
OL,8,F#18 billion a year, and the 900,000
OL,9,F"missing workers" could have caused a
OL,10,Floss of tax revenue of up to #4.5
OL,11,Fbillion in 2023, they add.
OL,13,FThe authors say that improving the
OL,14,Fnation's health could be an
OL,15,F"innovative strategy to revitalise the
OL,16,Feconomy".
OL,18,F"Better health will only be possible
OL,19,Fif we move from a sickness model of
OL,20,Fhealth policy to a health creation
OL,21,Fone," they wrote.
